text.お知らせがあるみたい！\r\nなんだろうな～、気になるな～っ♪:
Looks like there's an announcement! 
I wonder what it is～, I'm curious～♪
text.もうすぐイベントがあるらしいよ！\r\nカイチョーも参加するのかな～？:
I hear there's an event coming soon! 
I wonder if Kaichou will be there too～?
text.…今日も走んなきゃダメ？\r\nボク疲れちゃったんだけど～。:
Do I have to run today too? 
But I'm so tired～.
text.なんかね、体が\r\nうまく動かないんだ…。\r\nうぅ～っ、モヤモヤするなぁ…:
Somehow, my body's not moving well…. 
Ugh～, I don't feel so good…!
text.ふふんっ、無敵のテイオー様は\r\n今日もゼッコーチョー！ボクの\r\n走りを見:
Hehe, the invincible Teio-sama is in top 
form again today! Don't topple over 
in surprise when you see me run, eh～?
text.ねぇねぇ、今日のボク\r\nきっといつもよりすっごいよ！\r\n早く走らせて！早:
Hey hey, I'm feeling even stronger 
than usual today! I'm going to run 
faster! Faster faster faster!
text.ボクは準備オッケー！\r\nねぇねぇ、トレーナーは？まだ～？:
I'm ready! 
Hey hey, Trainer? You're still not～?
text.よ～し、やるぞ～！\r\nちゃんと見ててよね！:
Al～right, let's do it! 
Just watch me!
text.よ～し、絶好調！\r\nふふんっ、テイオー様の最強伝説は\r\n今回も破られそう:
Al～right, I'm in top condition! 
Hehe, Teio-sama's greatest legend 
isn't about to be broken this time!
text.ちゃんと見ててね、トレーナー！\r\nぱぱーっと勝ってくるから、\r\n瞬きした:
Watch carefully, trainer! 
I'll win in a flash; if you blink, 
you might miss it～
text.どうせボクが勝っちゃうし、\r\n今のうちに表彰台での台詞\r\n考えとこっかな:
I'm going to win anyway, 
so maybe I'll think of a line to 
say on the podium right now～♪
text.これからもよろしくねトレーナー！\r\n無敵のテイオー伝説には、\r\n絶対にキ:
Keep up the good work, Trainer! 
For the legend of the invincible Teio, 
you're absolutely necessary!
text.ねーぇー、カイチョー見なかった？\r\nも～っ、今日こそ一緒に\r\nお昼ご飯食:
Hey, have you seen Kaichou? 
Aw, I was thinking of having lunch 
with her today!
text.トレーナー、お疲れ様っ。\r\nうむうむ、今日もボクのために\r\nご苦労であ～:
Trainer, good job! 
Hmmm, you worked hard for me 
again today～♪
text.こんな時間にトレーナーも外出？\r\nボクはね、まだ体動かし足りない\r\nから:
Trainer's also out at this hour? 
I haven't done enough exercise yet,
so I was just hanging around～.
text.ねぇ～！ちょー強いカブトムシ、\r\n捕まえに行こうよ～！\r\nゴルシも持って:
Hey～! Let's go catch a strong beetle～! 
Golshi has one too～!
text.同学年の中でも、特にマックイーン\r\nには負けたくないんだ。テストでも\r\n:
Of my class, I especially don't want 
to lose to McQueen. Whether it's 
tests or races, I'll beat her～!
text.今度一緒にゲーセン行こっ！\r\nボク、どんなゲームでも\r\nトレーナーに勝て:
Let's go to the arcade together 
sometime! I'm confident I can beat 
Trainer at any game.
text.レースもいいけど、ダンスも最高だ\r\nよね～！みんなにすごーいって思わ\r\n:
Racing is good, but dancing is 
the best～! That's right, everyone 
thinks that both are amazing!
text.パパもママも、いっつも\r\n電話かけてくるんだ。そんなに\r\n心配しなくたっ:
Mom and dad call me all the time. 
They don't have to worry so much～.
text.ねぇねぇ、何か知りたいことある？\r\nふふふ…学園内のうわさ話には、\r\nち:
Hey hey, is there anything you wanna 
know? Hehehe… I'm a bit～ of an 
expert on academy gossip, you know?
text.ボクが目指すのは、誰にも負けない\r\n最強無敵の三冠ウマ娘！この服で、\r\n:
My goal is to be the undefeated, strongest, 
invincible triple crown horsegirl! 
In this outfit, I'll definitely make it come true!
text.見て見て～っ、この赤いマント！\r\n袖の模様も…えへへ、カイチョーと\r\nお:
Look, look at this red cloak! 
And the sleeves' pattern too… ehehe, 
I asked to match them with Kaichou♪
text.生徒会室のソファがフカフカでさ。\r\nお昼寝はあそこに限るんだけど…\r\nエ:
The student council room sofa is fluffy. 
I just take naps there but… 
Air Groove gets mad at me～.
text.眠れない時は、クラシックをよく\r\n聴くんだ～。退屈ですぐ寝ちゃえる\r\nか:
When I can't sleep, I listen to classical 
music. I get bored and fall asleep right 
away, I recommend it for Trainer too!
text.プールで飛び込み台から飛ぶと、\r\nすっっっごい気持ちいいんだ～！\r\n今度:
When you jump off the diving board 
into the pool, it feels soooo good～! 
Next time I'm trying the highest one♪
text.ねー、今日は何するの？\r\n早く始めようよ～っ！:
Hey～ what are we doing today? 
Hurry up, let's get started～!
text.トレーナー、次はどうするの？\r\nなんでもボクに任せてよ！:
Trainer, what's next? 
Whatever it is, leave it to me!
text.ストレッチしゅーりょー！\r\nボクね、体がすっごい柔らかい\r\nんだよ！ぐに:
Streeetch! 
My body's so soft! 
It's squishy!
text.よーし、トレーニングの時間だー！\r\nボクのすごいところ、\r\nしっかり見て:
Al～right, training time～! 
Watch my greatness closely!
text.すっっっごい厳しいトレーニング\r\nさせてよ！おねが～い！\r\nカイチョーが:
Let me try some reeeeally tough 
training! Pleease! 
Like Kaichou does!
text.最強のウマ娘になるまで\r\nボクは止まるつもりないよ！\r\nもちろんトレーナ:
I'm not stopping until I become 
the strongest horsegirl! 
Of course, Trainer won't either, right?
text.どうせボクが勝っちゃうし、今のうちに表彰台での台詞考えとこっかな～♪:
I'm going to win anyway, 
so maybe I'll think of a line to 
say on the podium right now～♪
text.3人が出たCM、カッコよかった！\r\n街並みが何か所か映ったでしょ、\r\n早:
That CM with the 3 of them was 
so cool! It showed some neat places 
in the city, right? I can't wait 
to go play there!
text.目指すなら当然、全員が笑顔な\r\nハッピーエンドじゃなきゃね！: Our goal should be to reach a happy \nend where everyone's smiling!
